From William Mayne Subject Re Christian Morality is In article Simon Clippingdale writes Dan I'm concerned that you are in grave spiritual danger because of your stubborn refusal to love and accept into your heart the Mighty Invisible Pink Nice parody I shall pray for In fact brother I cast out the demon which binds you in the Name of the Mighty Invisible Pink Dan you must have faith Then you better pray for me too because I believe that the Mighty Invisibile Pink Unicorn does not One being cannot be both Pink and The demon or should that be daemon that keeps me from believing and saving my soul is named Bill Mayne